nd oratorios his singing career is most notable for a twenty five year run as the evangelist in the passions of st john and matthew in the carmel bach festival the james schwabacher collection consists of sound recordings correspondence scores scrapbooks clippings programs teaching material and other papers view the finding aid here the collection was processed under the auspices of the national historical publications and records commission raymondh stanford edu's blog login to post comments music james schwabacher collection music library back stanford university stanford california 94305 650 725 1064 terms of use copyright complaints
